{"tid":1112337,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"學校講Talk注意事項","createTime":"2019-04-17T11:00:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T17:40:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e02c1bd013f6477835d23ac49d234835d8c62f3f","tid":1112337,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T11:00:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/曾志豪/daily/article/20190417/20657469\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E8%B1%AA%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190417%2F20657469&d=BZ3h%2BuUaIL2OU9i9OZdAr3dT8yuj5BXRLHKnqfTXFLo%3D&h=8b5bef61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E8%B1%AA%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190417%2F20657469&h=c4eefcc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/曾志豪/daily/article/20190417/20657469</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學校講Talk注意事項 - 曾志豪<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190417/large/e8808a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190417%2Flarge%2Fe8808a.jpg&h=dc8642b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n資料圖片(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n除非你是陳奕迅，否則你到學校講Talk遇到不專心的情況，也只能啞子吃黃連，不能發作怪責同學。<br />\n<br />\n我到過大學中學講Talk，基本上你要有心理準備：台下的同學是隨時會瞓覺走神。聽Talk瞓覺是定律。因為許多時候學校的講座都安排在1300之後，正是飯氣攻心、上了半天課的疲累時刻，除非你上台自帶荷里活電影爆破特技音響，否則在禮堂冷氣或者風扇帶動下，他們真的很快入睡。<br />\n<br />\n另一個心理準備便是，邀請你講Talk是老師而不是學生，即是說，覺得你有趣、好想聽你講嘢分享的人，是老師，而不是同學。<br />\n<br />\n所以講者千萬不要發怒：你地請我嚟講Talk點解自己又瞓晒覺？唔想聽唔好嚟啊嘛！<br />\n<br />\nSorry，講者們，同學如果可以選擇，他們還真的不想來，只是出於學校的安排，他們才現身。即是說，如果你的講題內容不是特別吸引，或者你沒有黃子華的棟篤笑功力，他們實在沒有必要應酬你。<br />\n<br />\n所以我每次到學校講Talk，我都告訴自己：他們現在只是肉身安坐，靈魂未歸位，我的目標便是希望講座完畢，可以用內容把他們的靈魂召來。<br />\n<br />\n我慣用技巧：開場白不要長篇大論，多些台下參與。例如問：我叫曾志豪，做香港電台「瘋Show快活人」。有無人聽過？舉手睇吓。「頭條新聞」有無睇過呢？我喺蘋果寫專欄，仲有無人會買報紙睇㗎？<br />\n<br />\n一連串的問題，讓同學覺得有份參與，需要表態，正常可以把睡意驅走。<br />\n<br />\n然後嘗試把你的主講題目，化成問題，交由同學回應。譬如你要講六四，可以先化成問題：知道六四係乜嘢嘅舉手。去過六四燭光集會嘅舉手。<br />\n<br />\n同學有份參與，容易集中精神。有了同學意見的鋪墊，你再講自己的講題，水到渠成。<br />\n<br />\n那天我在講座尾聲時問了同學一個問題：你鍾意依家嘅香港嗎？<br />\n<br />\n他們呆住了，但又忍不住互相討論。沒有標準答案，你又鍾意依家嘅香港咩呢？  <br />\n<br />\n曾志豪 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n烏鴉變監製 (馮睎乾)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n澳洲人的死腦筋 (高慧然)"},{"pid":"d9b2476ada5eb349f4cf636936e33f6823b34a5a","tid":1112337,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T11:08:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd2424828992634e68b630a5ffa1c964c4c53028","tid":1112337,"uid":220701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d9b2476ada5eb349f4cf636936e33f6823b34a5a","tid":1112337,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T11:08:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T11:22:43.000Z","msg":"有咩問題"},{"pid":"69bf3f7130c6cb499072268da29006a353bef06f","tid":1112337,"uid":84511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fd2424828992634e68b630a5ffa1c964c4c53028","tid":1112337,"uid":220701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d9b2476ada5eb349f4cf636936e33f6823b34a5a","tid":1112337,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T11:08:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T11:22:43.000Z","msg":"有咩問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T12:03:33.000Z","msg":"連登仔睇唔起呢啲跳躍式寫作手法<br />\n每篇議論文都一定要一環扣一環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7f3741a5285722474dd3345f1246a6d826a7611","tid":1112337,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9b2476ada5eb349f4cf636936e33f6823b34a5a","tid":1112337,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T11:08:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:15:57.000Z","msg":"戛然而止，餘韻猶存"},{"pid":"08ef5a4769e3433c02695d0bf92a788850f8f0f5","tid":1112337,"uid":82542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:21:44.000Z","msg":"好多talk都好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e452c8db56c0bfc801e4389aa5511da25f2aa423","tid":1112337,"uid":187196,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:40:03.000Z","msg":"上堂瞓教真係香港特有文化黎<br />\n我之前接待過某香港CC留學團，個professor 問我點解班學生可以上堂瞓教，我都唔知點答佢"}]}